ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model_Bag
ContainedObjects.Description: Use the dice included in this container to play Devil's Wheel - they are scaled to be proportional to using the base game dice with the box lid.

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model_Stack
ContainedObjects.Description:
While a Hero has 1 or more Unwanted Attention Markers, any time they roll a 7 on a location Event Chart, they must roll to see if they are attacked!

Roll a D6. If the roll is equal to or less than the number of Unwanted Attemtion Markers they have, the Hero is attacked from behind by a cowardly but dangerous individual, with murder on the mind!

ContainedObjects.Description: Discard to add D3 Damage to a single Hit. You also take 1 Wound, ignoring Defense.

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model_Stack

Shots: 1
+2 Damage

Although this is a Ranged Attack, use your Melee To Hit for the roll.
